title: Trump bus is turned into mobile artwork
text: Trump bus is turned into mobile artwork Buy Photo A campaign bus used for the presidential hopeful Donald Trump in Iowa was bought by t.Rutt a writer, entrepreneur, economist, and artist (according to his website). Artist Mike Stevens paints over the Turmp logos Monday Oct. 19, 2015, making it a mobile art piece per the instructions of artist t.Rutt.
